# Images Directory

Place your images here:

## Required Images:
- profile.jpg (400x500px) - Your profile photo for About section
- projects/project1.jpg (400x300px) - Project screenshot 1
- projects/project2.jpg (400x300px) - Project screenshot 2
- projects/project3.jpg (400x300px) - Project screenshot 3

## Recommended Image Formats:
- JPG/JPEG for photos
- PNG for logos and graphics with transparency
- WebP for optimized web images

## Image Optimization Tips:
- Compress images before uploading
- Use appropriate dimensions
- Consider using lazy loading for better performance
